      "role": "user",
      "content": "i was just looking at the stars and thinking about how everything is just... noise. like, in a billion years, none of this matters. none of our struggles, none of our \"love\" or \"pain\" even leaves a dent in the universe. it feels like we're just playing a game that was designed to be lost anyway. everything feels so pointless.",
