      "content": "but \"letting go\" feels like more than just finding solace. if everything is truly as indifferent and temporary as you say, and if human struggle is just a \"tiny, meaningless part\" of it... then why am i even trying to keep going? it feels like there's no real logic in fighting to stay in a system that doesn't even care if i'm here or not.",
